routeFacts.name: Hauptstrecke München – Augsburg
routeFacts.description: Hauptstrecke München – Augsburg is a route for Train Sim World 2. It features the 62 kilometre route between Munich and Augsburg with speeds of up to 230 km/h. Featured with the route is the DB BR 403 ICE 3 - a modern high speed EMU, and the DB BR 423 - an S-Bahn commuter EMU.
routeInfo: Hauptstrecke München – Augsburg covers the 62 kilometre route from München to Augsburg. The route has been upgraded for high speed operation, with maximum speed limits of 230 km/h. The route also includes the western half of Munich S-Bahn's S3 line from Mammendorf to München Hbf.
